<body>
  <h1>BCM Missionary Monthly Report System - Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 2025</p>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>PURPOSE OF THIS APP</h2>
    <p>
      This application is exclusively designed for <strong>Baptist Church of Mizoram (BCM)</strong> missionaries to submit their monthly ministry reports digitally.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>DATA COLLECTION</h2>
    <p>We collect only ministry-related information necessary for monthly reporting:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal identification (name, position, location).</li>
      <li>Ministry activities and statistics.</li>
      <li>Contact information for official correspondence.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>DATA STORAGE</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> All data is primarily stored on your device using a secure local database.</li>
      <li>Data remains under your control and can be deleted anytime.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>DATA USAGE</h2>
    <p>Your data is used solely for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Generating monthly ministry reports.</li>
      <li>Tracking ministry activities and progress.</li>
      <li>Official BCM reporting requirements.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>DATA SHARING</h2>
    <p>We do <strong>NOT</strong>:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Sell or share your data with third parties.</li>
      <li>Use your data for marketing purposes.</li>
      <li>Access your data without your consent.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>CLOUD SYNC</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>When signed in with Google:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Data syncs automatically when internet is available.</li>
        <li>Encrypted transmission to secure Firebase servers.</li>
        <li>Access limited to your account only.</li>
        <li>You can disable cloud sync at any time.</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>YOUR RIGHTS</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access all your stored data.</li>
      <li>Export your reports in various formats.</li>
      <li>Delete your data permanently.</li>
      <li>Opt-out of cloud sync (use local storage only).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>SECURITY</h2>
    <p>We protect your data through:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Device-level security (PIN/password/biometric).</li>
      <li>No unauthorized access to your reports.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>GOOGLE SERVICES</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>When using Google Sign-In:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>We use Google Firebase for authentication and cloud storage.</li>
        <li>Googleâ€™s privacy policy applies for authentication data: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a></li>
        <li>You can revoke Google access through your Google Account settings.</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section contact">
    <h2>CONTACT</h2>
